name: Mooncake Rush
description:
Join Jack Jade the Jade Rabbit on his quest to the moon! Arrive to the Cold Palace before midnight to do your share of the work before Mid Autum runs out, and enjoy the mooncakes and starry eggs along the way!

NOTE: We are a execs/professional major team, so we're not qualified or entering for prizes!!!!

Re-uploading back to V1 (submitted at 17:58) for fairness.

All assets are self-made by the team (art, music).
